'''ONE News''' is the news division of New Zealand television network, [[TVNZ]]. The service is [[live broadcast]], from [[TVNZ Centre]] in [[Auckland, New Zealand|Auckland]]. The flagship news bulletin is the nightly 6pm news hour, but ''ONE News'' also has midday, afternoon and late night news bulletins, as well as [[current affairs (news format)|current affairs]] shows such as Breakfast and Close Up.
